      <textAnnotation id="sid-DC6FA89C-4F5A-4D88-BBD3-408B0BECD7EB" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>1. Sales Area (Sales organization, Distribution channel, Division) should be available during sales order creation
2. Customer Pricing Procedure will be derived from "Sold to Party" 
3. Pricing Procedure will be derived from Sales Order type 
4. For internal PO SO Process order type ZICO will be used with unique Document Pricing Procedure so that separate Pricing Procedure will be determined (Cost+)</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-7397DDBB-A053-40DF-804D-DAEC69D5F890" signavio:alignment="left">
